<doc docid="CNS_CMN_20070702.0702" genre="text" sysid="source">
<hl>
<seg id="1"> 穆里尼奥坚 称 将 留守 <LOCATION english="Chelsea " believable=false>切尔西</LOCATION> <NUMBER english="60" believable=true>60</NUMBER> 岁 前 彻底 退出 足坛 </seg>
