</seg>
</hl>
<p>
<seg id="2"> 本报 <LOCATION english="Washington " believable=false>华盛顿</LOCATION> <TIME english="July 22|July 22nd" believable=true>7月22日</TIME> 电 ( 记者 徐 <PERSON english="Qisheng" believable=false>启生</PERSON> ) </seg>
